Paper: hep-th/9302089

Date: 1993-02-19

Title: The Hidden Quantum Group of the 8-vertex Free Fermion Model

AlgebrasAuthors: R.Cuerno, C.Gomez, E.Lopez and G.Sierra

Comments: 8 pages, Latex, IMAFF-2/93 (several typos corrected; some comments

added)Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B307 (1993) 56-60

We prove in this paper that the elliptic $R$--matrix of the eight vertex freefermion model is the intertwiner $R$--matrix of a quantum deformedClifford--Hopf algebra. This algebra is constructed by affinization of aquantum Hopf deformation of the Clifford algebra.